OL,6,Fended up passing unopposed without a
OL,7,Fformal vote after the Government
OL,8,Fpulled its participation.
OL,10,FIt marked the first time the Commons
OL,11,Fformally backed an immediate ceasefire
OL,12,Fin Gaza, though the Government does
OL,13,Fnot have to adopt the position as the
OL,14,Fvote is not binding.
